{{vgname|戰神：諸神黃昏|en=God of War: Ragnarök}}是由[[索尼互動娛樂聖塔莫尼卡工作室|聖塔莫尼卡工作室]]開發、[[索尼互動娛樂|索尼互動娛樂]]發行的[[動作冒險遊戲|動作冒險]][[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]，預計於2022年在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]平台獨佔發售。該遊戲為「[[戰神系列|戰神系列]]」第九部作品以及2018年《[[戰神_(2018年遊戲)|戰神]]》的續作，與前作一樣以[[北歐神話|北歐神話]]為基礎，古代[[挪威|挪威]]為背景。故事主題將圍繞使北歐神話終結的「[[諸神黃昏|諸神黃昏]]」。

== 發展 ==
本作在2018年遊戲《[[戰神_(2018年遊戲)|戰神]]》遊戲結束時以暗示「[[諸神的黃昏|諸神黃昏]]即將到來」，以及一個隱藏結局，[[索爾|雷神索爾]]將與[[克雷多斯_(戰神)|克雷多斯]]和[[阿特柔斯|阿特柔斯]]大戰。儘管當時並未正式宣布推出新遊戲，但遊戲總監{{le|科里·巴羅格|Cory Barlog}}確認《戰神》並不是克雷多斯的最後一個遊戲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/god-of-war-ps4-doesnt-include-multiplayer-wont-be-/1100-6441104/|title=God of War PS4 Doesn't Include Multiplayer, Won't Be Kratos's Last Game|date=2016-06-21|last=Paget|first=Mat|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2016-06-21|archive-date=2018-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413193804/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/god-of-war-ps4-doesnt-include-multiplayer-wont-be-/1100-6441104/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來又透露，未來的戰神遊戲的背景將繼續設置北歐中，[[阿特柔斯|阿特柔斯]]（[[洛基|洛基]]）亦將在遊戲中出現<ref>{{cite news|publisher=Finder|url=https://www.finder.com.au/god-of-war-5-norse|title=Sony confirms God of War 5 will also be set in Norse mythology|date=2018-04-08|accessdate=2018-04-09|first=Chris|last=Stead|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109030103/https://www.finder.com.au/god-of-war-5-norse|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本作於2020年9月16日的[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]發佈會上正式宣布將於2021年在PlayStation 5上發售<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-ps5-announce/|title=God of War 2 is official, and it's called God of War: Ragnarok|date=2020-09-16|last1=Sheridan|first1=Connor|last2=Weber|first2=Rachel|work=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]]|publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]]|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022110459/https://www.gamesradar.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-ps5-announce/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/ps5-god-of-war-2-sequel|title=God of War Ragnarok Announced for PS5|date=2020-09-16|last=Kim|first=Matt T. M.|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]]|accessdate=2020-09-16|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917104850/https://www.ign.com/articles/ps5-god-of-war-2-sequel|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/god-of-war-2-ragnarok-announced-at-ps5-event/1100-6482261/|title=God Of War 2: Ragnarok Announced At PS5 Event|date=2020-09-16|last=Watts|first=Steve|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2020-09-16}}</ref>。前作的主要角色[[弗蕾亚|弗蕾亚]]（[[弗丽嘉|弗丽嘉]]）、[[密米爾|密米尔]]將會回歸，新的北歐神話角色包括[[安格爾波達|安格爾波達]]、[[杜林_(北歐神話)|杜林]]、[[提爾|提爾]]和[[索爾|索爾]]。

